# Architecture

## System Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    Channels["Channels\nWhatsApp, Telegram, Slack, ..."] --> OC["OpenClaw Node\nDigiMe agent"]
    Users --> UI["UI\nNext.js Â· Cloud Run"]

    OC --> GW["Webhook Gateway\nChannel adapter"]
    GW --> API["API\nFastAPI Â· GKE"]
    UI --> API
    GW --> Pipeline["Webhook Pipeline\nNATS + 40 agents"]
    API -- callbacks --> Pipeline
    Pipeline -- stores results --> API

    API --> Storage["Storage\nGCS / Supabase / local"]
    API --> Neo4j["Neo4j\nGraphiti knowledge graph"]
    Pipeline -- entities/rels --> API -- dual-write --> Neo4j
```

